children.name: AWS - All - S3 - Public Bucket Alert
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=*cloudtrail* (PutBucketAcl)
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.AccessControlPolicy.Owner.DisplayName" as AWSAccount
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.bucketName" as BucketName
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.AccessControlPolicy.AccessControlList.Grant[1].Grantee.URI" as requestParameters_URI
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.AccessControlPolicy.AccessControlList.Grant[1].Permission" as requestParameters_Permission
| where requestParameters_URI matches "http://acs.amazonaws.com/groups/global/AllUsers" and requestParameters_Permission = "READ"

| json field=_raw "userIdentity.userName" as UserName

panels.name: Modified Public Objects by Object-Bucket
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*cloudtrail* (PutObjectAcl)
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.accountId" as AWSAccount
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.userName" as UserName
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.accessKeyId" as AccessKeyId
| json field=_raw "awsRegion" as AWSRegion
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.bucketName" as BucketName
| json field=_raw "resources[0].ARN" as ObjectName
| concat(ObjectName,"-",BucketName) as Object_Bucket
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.AccessControlPolicy.AccessControlList.Grant[1].Grantee.URI" as requestParameters_URI
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.AccessControlPolicy.AccessControlList.Grant[1].Permission" as requestParameters_Permission
| where requestParameters_URI matches "http://acs.amazonaws.com/groups/global/AllUsers" and requestParameters_Permission = "READ"
| timeslice 1h
| count by Object_Bucket, _timeslice
| transpose row _timeslice column Object_Bucket
